1, Open http://zespia.tw/hexo/docs/

2, Install Git follow the directions

3, Install Node.js follow the directions

4, Open Node.js command, 
	
$ npm install -g hexo


5,cd to the folder which will be the root folder of hexo project.
$ hexo init

6,  change _config.xml, add this for deploy

deploy:
  type: github
  repository: https://github.com/Viyu/viyu.github.com.git
  branch: master

7, copy ENAME file to ./source.

8, cd to /source/

 delete ./_posts if thers is no files to keep.

 $git clone https://github.com/Viyu/_posts.git 


9, cd.. to ./

$ hexo generate

$ hexo server

add new .md in ./source.

$ hexo deploy

10, cd to source
